---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms"
  description="Terms for using ATSocy, the ATSocy relay, and ATSocy-hosted media uploads."
>
  <section class="xnn-container-page max-w-3xl space-y-8">
    <header class="space-y-3">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-fg">Terms</h1>
      <p class="max-w-2xl text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-600">
        These terms apply to ATSocy's services, including the website, the public relay at
        <code>relay.atsocy.com</code>, and the media server at <code>media.atsocy.com</code>.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-7 text-neutral-700">
      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-fg">Acceptable use</h2>
        <p>
          Do not use these services to publish, upload, or distribute unlawful material,
          malware, spam, harassment, infringement, or content that creates unreasonable operational
          or legal risk for the service operator.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-fg">Moderation and removal</h2>
        <p>
          ATSocy may remove files, reports, events, or accounts at its discretion to respond to
          abuse, legal requests, moderation needs, storage pressure, or policy changes. Access to
          upload privileges may also be limited, revoked, or gated in the future.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-fg">Service availability</h2>
        <p>
          This infrastructure is provided on an as-is basis. Availability, retention,
          storage limits, and supported features may change without notice. Do not rely on ATSocy
          as your sole copy of important data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-fg">User responsibility</h2>
        <p>
          You are responsible for the Nostr keys you use, the content you publish, and any rights
          needed to upload or distribute that content. ATSocy may preserve records needed to
          investigate misuse or comply with legal obligations.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-fg">No guarantee of confidentiality</h2>
        <p>
          These relay and media services are public-facing infrastructure. They are not
          offered as confidential storage. Operators may inspect data and logs when needed for
          moderation, incident response, and maintenance.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
